{"tid":526784,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"其實做抑鬱病人既屋企人都好辛苦","createTime":"2018-01-12T03:27:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-27T15:03:00.000Z","uid":156983,"like":47,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"3eac4bb6bb95aa31381bb1b913c443978e8b9468","tid":526784,"uid":156983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T03:27:51.000Z","msg":"因學業壓力 晚晚喺度喊 要媽媽陪住訓 陪到兩三點有時都仲未喊攰 其他人就算係自己房都比佢嘈醒 第二日都冇乜精神返工返學<br />\n前個排佢直程停課 先叫做好似正常返 <br />\n聖誕過後佢自己要求轉校 屋企人個個贊成 等佢有學習新環境<br />\n點知又話驚新同學 驚識唔到新朋友 樣樣野都要自己處理 又日日lay喺自己間房...變返以前咁<br />\n<br />\n屋企人其實好多時已經就哂佢<br />\n佢喊 安慰佢 就算冇安慰 都唔會直接鬧佢<br />\n唔返學又鼓勵佢 <br />\n<br />\n早幾日同佢傾： <em>大個喇 好多時自己要學識獨立 咁出到社會 起碼可以自己照顧自己呀 etc. 就由自己每朝早自己著校服呢d小事開始練下... </em><br />\n佢話： <em>你鬧我呀？你宜家都唔尊重我！我食藥㗎...</em><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我有時覺得佢係港女+抑鬱既合體 病發還病發 有時無事既時候都恃住個病要人服侍<br />\n<br />\n我真係唔知可以點 媽媽一早崩潰左<br />\n<br />\nSorry for 1999"},{"pid":"afe9c6b6e2b440427b263f5ea5c285cd7d094786","tid":526784,"uid":19072,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T04:10:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"518477d281dd75accb5b582c86d167bd85f7cbf1","tid":526784,"uid":88437,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T07:30:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 睇得出樓主都好在意呢個家人,但係同時都覺得好攰. <br />\n照顧有情緒病既家人真係唔輕鬆.<br />\n不過樓主如果因為咁而壓力大好辛苦,都要同朋友或者同巴絲傾訴下!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同媽媽互相支持鼓勵都係一個力量黎!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果有機會,可能係盡量唔傷害家人自尊咁同佢傾多D? 當佢做到小小既進步,例如著衫,沖涼,落街買野咁都讚下佢,令佢肯繼續做,做多D?"},{"pid":"b24de00101dbd4c3bb412031174912a43c62453d","tid":526784,"uid":108249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T07:33:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60cb96ed1e1e34eede1eda266eb77433a63ceab6","tid":526784,"uid":156983,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"518477d281dd75accb5b582c86d167bd85f7cbf1","tid":526784,"uid":88437,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T07:30:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 睇得出樓主都好在意呢個家人,但係同時都覺得好攰. <br />\n照顧有情緒病既家人真係唔輕鬆.<br />\n不過樓主如果因為咁而壓力大好辛苦,都要同朋友或者同巴絲傾訴下!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同媽媽互相支持鼓勵都係一個力量黎!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果有機會,可能係盡量唔傷害家人自尊咁同佢傾多D? 當佢做到小小既進步,例如著衫,沖涼,落街買野咁都讚下佢,令佢肯繼續做,做多D?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T08:59:38.000Z","msg":"多謝你嘅鼓勵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  以為連登個個都咁無情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n我諗最重要都係食藥同比d耐性 因為其實我地做咩講咩 佢都只會係諗埋一邊 even讚佢 佢都覺得你好假<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82458f0a9dfb193af52abcbbae37ae3ceb026bb5","tid":526784,"uid":167359,"like":18,"dislike":2,"score":16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T09:05:43.000Z","msg":"辛苦在有咩事都用個病在擋箭牌"},{"pid":"13c96b9200c1e6f2a705239892823b520cf1f105","tid":526784,"uid":16668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T09:10:14.000Z","msg":"幫你唔到但睇字都feel 到辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ,成日咁樣你屋企人會唔會有次忍唔住屌佢"},{"pid":"8056f0adee6cc246b5540690ac1bd5c3a2e7cf4e","tid":526784,"uid":155818,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T09:10:27.000Z","msg":"幾歲呀?個病幾時開始?<br />\n無可能照顧到佢一世架喎"},{"pid":"dcbf6632a73f147871a6a00bbe06fa5431b3643a","tid":526784,"uid":118945,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T09:17:20.000Z","msg":"巴打有無鼓勵佢搵專業人士例如醫生？<br />\n聽你咁講情況好似好嚴重，長遠可能影響一家人嘅關係㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果可以鼓勵佢睇醫生，食藥可能改善到抑鬱症狀，加上有時候有啲安慰說話或者道理由家人講，可能未係最適合<br />\n加油啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20bfe01db0a5cb8adad7f50e00e12b104ea2ba73","tid":526784,"uid":31708,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T10:08:28.000Z","msg":"以前我就係果個抑鬱病人<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又係直頭返唔到學<br />\n其實講乜都無用 藥物就有小小幫助<br />\n最重要係病人本身想唔想改變 <br />\n我依家就半工讀補返以前無讀書既學歷<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb7780e142aad5d85503db5131dcc31e15ce53f8","tid":526784,"uid":156983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"82458f0a9dfb193af52abcbbae37ae3ceb026bb5","tid":526784,"uid":167359,"like":18,"dislike":2,"score":16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T09:05:43.000Z","msg":"辛苦在有咩事都用個病在擋箭牌"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T19:12:21.000Z","msg":"Totally agree! 我覺得佢抑鬱crossover公主病<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9213e0cb25aea7359ab87ed504e09239e1f49147","tid":526784,"uid":27251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T19:14:46.000Z","msg":"我什麼都冇同屋企人講 雖然唔係好嚴重 但是好難過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd857d923a91485e264f9917785a62f214311bf5","tid":526784,"uid":156983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"13c96b9200c1e6f2a705239892823b520cf1f105","tid":526784,"uid":16668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T09:10:14.000Z","msg":"幫你唔到但睇字都feel 到辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ,成日咁樣你屋企人會唔會有次忍唔住屌佢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T19:15:10.000Z","msg":"個病啱啱開始 Daddy咪好躁囉 日喊夜喊 之後已經習慣哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"561121f08b5f141681979a4ad820ed363fe929d6","tid":526784,"uid":2295,"like":1,"dislike":0,"